About this item

  • STRAIGHT FIT: Fitted through the hip and thigh with a straight leg. Sits at the waist.
  • LIGHT-STRETCH DENIM: Mid-weight cotton denim with a bit of stretch for all-day comfort. Comes in indigo denim washes or solid colors with a garment wash for a lived in denim-inspired look.
  • STRAIGHT JEAN: These classic, five-pocket jeans are a wardrobe workhorse, perfect for business casual or everyday on-the-go.
  • DETAILS: Features zippered fly with metal button fly closure, bartack reinforcements, and rivets at front hand pockets. With stretch denim, it is always recommended to hang to dry for an extended garment life.
  • LEG OPENING: 7 3/4" on US size 32.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Learn more how customers reviews work on Amazon

Customers say

Customers find these jeans comfortable with great build and material, and appreciate their appearance, with one noting they can be dressed up or down. The fit and quality receive positive feedback, and customers consider them good value for money. Regarding durability, while some say they're holding up well, others report issues with rips around the genitals. Customers disagree on the sizing, with some finding them roomy while others say they run slightly small, and similarly, opinions on stretchiness vary between those who love the fabric and those who find it not flexible enough.
